title: CRED REA Fish Team Belt Transect Survey at Oahu, Main Hawaiian Islands, 2006
name: cred-rea-fish-team-belt-transect-survey-at-oahu-main-hawaiian-islands-2006
notes: Belt transects along 3 consecutively-placed, 25m transect lines were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 2 sites at Oahu in the Main Hawaiian Islands (MHI) during July 27 - August 20 2006 in the NOAA Hi'ialakai (HI0610) Reef Assessment and Monitoring Program (RAMP) Cruise. Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
